@startuml
actor Client
participant Automatic
participant TicketSystem
participant Employee

Client -> Automatic: choose area and insert money
Automatic -> TicketSystem: create_ticket()
TicketSystem --> Automatic: returns ticket number
Automatic --> Client: issue ticket
Client -> Employee: enter swimming center
Employee -> Client: verify ticket / grant access
Employee --> Client: if not allowed, request to leave
@enduml
